  <summary>4/29/2003--Passed House amended.
Commends Operation Respect (a nonprofit organization engaged in a national effort to transform after-school programs and children's summer camps into more compassionate and respectful environments) and the "Don't Laugh At Me" program for their contributions to the sound academic focus, character development, and improved physical safety of children throughout the United States.</summary>
